  <steps>
    <step num="0">Heat oil in a large pot over high heat. </step>
    <step num="1">Cook the chicken until no pink is showing. </step>
    <step num="2">Add the garlic, bacon, spinach, salt, and pepper, cooking until spinach is wilted. </step>
    <step num="3">Pour in the cream and bring to a boil. </step>
    <step num="4">Add the pasta, cheese, and parsley, stirring until the pasta is coated evenly. </step>
    <step num="5">Enjoy! </step>
